<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>TrackSafe - Welcome</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
   body {
    background-image: url("/bg.jpg"); /* NO dot-slash */
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    height: 80vh;
    width: 60vw;
    margin: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  }


   .overlay {
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); /* semi-transparent dark overlay */
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  height: 100vh;
  width: 100vw;
  z-index: 1;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 50px;
}


    h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 40px;
      color: #f8f9fa;
    }

    p, li {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #e2e6ea;
    }

    ul {
      text-align: left;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-left: 30px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #a3c9a8;
      border-color: #a3c9a8;
      font-size: 18px;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #90b993;
      border-color: #90b993;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="overlay">
    <div class="content-box">
      <h1>TrackSafe: Train Anomaly Detection System</h1>
      <p>
        TrackSafe is a smart safety platform designed to detect anomalies in train operations using real-time input data such as speed, signal visibility, weather, brake status, and more.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Real-time prediction using machine learning</li>
        <li>Easy-to-use form-based input</li>
        <li>Supports dynamic feedback for enhanced safety</li>
        <li>Seamless integration with a FastAPI backend for rapid response</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Make train journeys safer, smarter, and more reliable with TrackSafe.
      </p>
      <a href="/form" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3">Continue</a>
    </div>
  </div>
